      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VALEDOR (7) Street Boss colt from the handy mare Earth Angel on debut for the Messara & Gavranich yard. Has looked sharp in his last two trial wins and gets every chance from the inside gate. TARRANT COUNTY (6) big improver second up after the long break with a fast finishing third over 1300m at Narromine. Has further upside with genuine top three prospects. NULKABA STAR (4) fighting second two back at Gosford, then flopped badly after racing without cover for a tiring fifth over 1250m at Taree on the heavy (10) surface. Good set-up today and worth thought. MAGIC MERLIN (3) resumes after showing a stack of ability in his first prep. Fitted with the one trial and don't dismiss.",
